Prerequisites

Install Ced_PwaApi module on your magento 2 
 (Place folders inside Ced_PwaApi inside your magento 2 root directory) 
 run below commands 
    php bin/magento setup:upgrade
    php bin/magento setup:static-content:deploy
    php bin/magento setup:di:compile

Install NodeJS >=10.14.1 LTS
Install Yarn >=1.13.0

place pwa_studio folder in parallel of magento 2 root directory

run below commands from pwa-studio folder

yarn install 
yarn run build 

inside pwa_studio/packages/ced-concept/.env
update MAGENTO_BACKEND_URL with your magento2 website url 

yarn run build 
yarn run stage:ced





